thread.title: BRIEF-Nedap FY Revenue Up At 182.2 Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nedap FY Revenue Up At 182.2 Million Euros
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - NEDAP:
* FY RECURRING REVENUES EUR 30.9 MILLION VERSUS EUR 25.4 MLN YEAR AGO
* FY EBITDA EUR 0.6‍​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 1.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 DIVIDEND EUR 2.5 PER SHARE * FY PROFIT AFTER TAXES EUR ‍​ 28.0 MILLION VERSUS EUR 10.8 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY OPERATING INCOME EXCLUDING ONE-OFFS EUR 15.9 MILLION VERSUS EUR 12.2 MILLION YEAR AGO
* EXPECTS INCOME TO INCREASE FURTHER IN 2018‍​ * FY REVENUE EUR 182.2 MILLION VERSUS EUR 163.2 MILLION YEAR AGO Source text : bit.ly/2o6yiDM Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
